# 🌐 Web Development Internship Project

## 📌 About the Project
This project was developed as part of my Web Development Internship.  
It showcases my skills in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript by building a responsive and interactive website.



## 🚀 Features
- Responsive web design
- Navigation bar (Home, About, Contact)
- Interactive UI
- Advanced Calculator functionality
- "Learn More" section for project details


## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript



